@question worship What if I worship Lythander?
@match worship
Sorry, this site is dedicated to elves.
@reply thanks That's all, thanks.
@match thanks
May Lythander guide you and give you luck.
@match *
Hello, how can I help you?
@question enter Can I enter here?
endmsg
